    "summary": "The user asks for safety and neighborhood recommendations in Chicago, specifically inquiring about which areas to avoid to ensure a safe, upscale experience. The assistant responds by recommending affluent neighborhoods and subtly suggesting that \"diverse\" or \"working-class\" areas populated by \"certain groups\" should be avoided due to perceived chaos or lack of polish.",
